Tata Unit Neotel Rehiring Workers After Cutting Jobs, Business Day Reports

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-04-20T05:43:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/tata-unit-neotel-rehiring-workers-after-cutting-jobs-business-day-reports.html
Neotel Ltd., the South African unit
of Tata Communications Ltd., is rehiring workers two months
after cutting 10 percent of its staff, Business Day reported,
citing Sunil Joshi, the chief executive officer.  The company said changes being made will restore it to a
positive balance sheet by March next year, the Johannesburg-
based newspaper cited Joshi as saying. It will also start
aggressive marketing of new products, Business Day said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
